('WATER STRIDER', 'A large aquatic insect that walks on the surface tension of still water. Completely harmless. Their sudden departure from a water surface indicates something large moving beneath.', 'RIVER / COASTAL / FRESHWATER', 'SMALLER / GAME', 'Elemental', 'global'),
