('WHITE-RUNE APEX-URUS', 'A pale tundra strain of the great Runebear with black claws and a roar that carries for miles over snow; stalks caribou, mammoth-calves, and unwary sled teams.', 'TUNDRA', 'AGGRESSIVE / PREDATORY', 'Beast', 'global'),
